FBIS4-18144 "drweu062_j_94007" FBIS-WEU-94-062 Daily Report 30 Mar 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Martinazzoli Resigns From Italian Popular Party Martinazzoli Resigns From Italian Popular Party LD3003130994 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1242 GMT 30 Mar 94 LD3003130994 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Italian BFN [Excerpts] Mino Martinazzoli, the secretary of the Italian Popular Party has written a letter of resignation to the party chairman Rosa Russo Jervolino. [passage omitted] His spokesman Marco Giudici confirmed that the resignation is official and irrevocable. Jervolino will hold a news conference at the party's headquarters at 1800.
